  &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1em; color: #000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;üìâ&lt;/span&gt;¬†&lt;a href="https://javascriptweekly.com/link/180123/rss" title="www.repoflow.io" style=" color: #3366aa;    font-size: 1.05em;"&gt;Node.js 16 to 25 Benchmarked Version-by-Version&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; ‚Äî The jumps in performance in various areas are striking (with Node 25, especially), with other areas getting more modest¬†gains.&lt;/p&gt;
