&lt;p&gt;üìÑ &lt;a href="https://javascriptweekly.com/link/180127/rss" style=" color: #3366aa; font-weight: 500 !important;   "&gt;My Opinionated ESLint Setup for Vue Projects&lt;/a&gt; ‚Äì Packed with examples to pick and choose¬†from. &lt;cite&gt;Alexander Opalic&lt;/cite&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üìÑ &lt;a href="https://javascriptweekly.com/link/180128/rss" style=" color: #3366aa; font-weight: 500 !important;   "&gt;A Scroll-Revealed WebGL Gallery with GSAP, Three.js, Astro and Barba.js&lt;/a&gt; ‚Äì Striking visual image reveal effect with &lt;a href="https://javascriptweekly.com/link/180129/rss" style=" color: #3366aa; font-weight: 500 !important;   "&gt;a live¬†demo.&lt;/a&gt; &lt;cite&gt;Chakib Mazouni&lt;/cite&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
