&lt;p&gt;üé§ &lt;a href="https://javascriptweekly.com/link/180131/rss" style=" color: #3366aa; font-weight: 500 !important;   "&gt;Securing npm is Table Stakes&lt;/a&gt;  &lt;cite&gt;Nicholas C. Zakas (Changelog Podcast)&lt;/cite&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
